data.description: This beautiful move-in ready home is nestled in the quiet gated community of European Grove in Northwest Fresno. It has a prime location within the neighborhood, next to one of the many community green spaces. You will feel at home from the moment you walk in! The living room has a cozy fireplace and is open to the kitchen and dining area. The home offers ample natural light coming from many windows. The gorgeous kitchen boasts stainless steel newer appliances, granite countertops and a sizable island with a breakfast bar. The backyard has a covered patio, extended concrete and a wooden deck that serves great as a BBQ area. The community offers many green spaces, shaded picnic tables and a putting green. You will enjoy the low maintenance front and backyard landscaping and indoor laundry. Take a private tour of this wonderful property today!
